OL,3,CFour in court charged with murder of a
OL,4,C17-year-old
OL,6,FThree men have appeared in Newport
OL,7,FMagistrates Court this morning
OL,8,Falongside a woman after the death of a
OL,9,Fteenager in Caerphilly County.
OL,11,FRicardo Elliot, 26, Connor Palfrey,
OL,12,F24, and Georgie Mears, 18, were in the
OL,13,Fdock alongside Elexi Manny, 24, all
OL,14,Fcharged with murder.
OL,16,F17-year-old Tristan Shae Kerr was
OL,17,Ffound with a serious injury on Lower
OL,18,FFrancis Street in Abertridwr on the
OL,19,Fevening of Thursday, 5 February.
