OL,6,FHe was later pronounced dead at the
OL,7,Fscene and police launched a murder
OL,8,Finvestigation.
OL,10,FRicardo Elliot and Georgie Mears
OL,11,Fappeared first in court, where they
OL,12,Fspoke only to give their names, dates
OL,13,Fof birth and addresses.
OL,15,FThere was shouting from the public
OL,16,Fgallery as the pair were led from the
OL,17,Fdock.
