OL,3,CFour in court charged with murder of a
OL,4,C17-year-old
OL,6,FNext, Connor Palfrey and Elexi Manny
OL,7,Fwere brought before the judge where
OL,8,Fagain they spoke only to confirm their
OL,9,Fnames, dates of birth and addresses.
OL,11,FBoth defendants wore grey jumpers and
OL,12,Ftrousers. Manny appeared tearful as
OL,13,Fshe was led into the dock.
OL,15,FAll four defendants were remanded in
OL,16,Fcustody and will appear at Cardiff
OL,17,FCrown Court tomorrow morning.
