OL,6,FA 28-year-old woman from Hereford who
OL,7,Fwas arrested on suspicion of assisting
OL,8,Fan offender has now been released
OL,9,Funder investigation.
OL,11,FSpecially trained officers from Gwent
OL,12,FPolice are supporting Tristan's family.
OL,14,FDetective Chief Inspector Jitka
OL,15,FTomkova-Griffiths said:
OL,17,F"We understand that there has been a
OL,18,Fgreat deal of interest in this
OL,19,Finvestigation, however we would ask
OL,20,Fpeople not to speculate about the
OL,21,Fidentities of those involved.
